learning_outcomes.en:
After completing the course the students will be able to
- hold a conversation on everyday topics without preparation;
- use simple language structures to describe their experience, meals and eating, customs of holidays and anniversaries, ask for help;
- explain/justify their points of view;
- talk about what they have heard or seen if the subject is familiar to them;
- undestand simple conversations by native speakers

grade_preconditions.et:
Kohustuslik osavõtt õppetööst vähemalt 80% ulatuses;
Testide (51% õigeid vastuseid) ja kodutööde sooritamine;
Suulise osa läbimine (jututund)
Kodulugemise (25 lk) nõuetekohane vastamine;
Tööde õigeaegne ja nõuetekohane esitamine.
